long.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G: This extension has been developed as part of a research study that will be managed by PLEX Lab research team at New Mexico State University. The extension is meant to be used by normal YouTube viewers to Augment the regular video page for research purposes by adding an overlay over the video player to show demonetized keywords. The videos we will be testing with are videos were mentioned by their creators that YouTube demonetized them. The extension is not meant to collect any data from the viewers. It is meant to collect their feedback when exposing a hidden metadata about the video they are watching such as the demonetized keywords.
